hopobject.body: What's the current interest rate for personal loans? rexavar symptoms Among the male smokers, those who lived in states where there was a cigarette tax increase moderately reduced their alcohol intake and the frequency of their binge drinking. Male smokers who experienced a tax hike drank 11 percent less in one sitting and binged on average seven fewer times per year compared with male smokers who did not experience a tax change. The study found no significant change in drinking behavior among nonsmokers and female smokers.
